hwMeta.bodyText:
If(clk._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0),
        write_ptr(0),
        read_ptr0(0),
        looped0(0)
    ).Else(
        write_ptr(write_ptr_next),
        read_ptr0(read_ptr0_next),
        looped0(looped0_next)
    )
)

If(reqLen > 255,
    a_len(255),
    sig_sizeRmFifo_dataIn_rem(0),
    sig_sizeRmFifo_dataIn_propagateLast(0)
).Else(
    a_len(sig_0),
    sig_sizeRmFifo_dataIn_rem(reqRem),
    sig_sizeRmFifo_dataIn_propagateLast(1)
)

If(lastReqDispatched._eq(1),
    a_addr(driver_req_addr),
    r_addr_next((driver_req_addr._reinterpret_cast(Bits(32, signed=False)) + 2048)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(32))),
    reqLen(driver_req_len),
    reqRem(driver_req_rem),
    remBackup_next(driver_req_rem),
    driver_req_rd(sig_sizeRmFifo_dataIn_rd & a_ready),
    sig_sizeRmFifo_dataIn_vld(driver_req_vld & a_ready),
    a_valid(driver_req_vld & sig_sizeRmFifo_dataIn_rd & ~rErrFlag)
).Else(
    driver_req_rd(0),
    a_addr(r_addr),
    If(ar_ack._eq(1),
        r_addr_next((r_addr._reinterpret_cast(Bits(32, signed=False)) + 2048)._reinterpret_cast(Bits(32)))
    ).Else(
        r_addr_next(r_addr)
    ),
    reqLen(lenDebth),
    reqRem(remBackup),
    sig_sizeRmFifo_dataIn_vld(a_ready),
    a_valid(sig_sizeRmFifo_dataIn_rd & ~rErrFlag),
    remBackup_next(remBackup)
)

If(lastReqDispatched._eq(1),
    ar_ack(driver_req_vld & sig_sizeRmFifo_dataIn_rd & a_ready),
    req_idBackup_next(driver_req_id),
    a_id(driver_req_id)
).Else(
    ar_ack(sig_sizeRmFifo_dataIn_rd & a_ready),
    a_id(req_idBackup),
    req_idBackup_next(req_idBackup)
)

If((r_valid & r_last & sig_sizeRmFifo_dataOut_propagateLast)._eq(1),
    Switch(sig_sizeRmFifo_dataOut_rem)\
        .Case(0,
            driver_r_strb(255))\
        .Case(1,
            driver_r_strb(1))\
        .Case(2,
            driver_r_strb(3))\
        .Case(3,
            driver_r_strb(7))\
        .Case(4,
            driver_r_strb(15))\
        .Case(5,
            driver_r_strb(31))\
        .Case(6,
            driver_r_strb(63))\
        .Case(7,
            driver_r_strb(127))
).Else(
    driver_r_strb(255)
)
